        <ontology:hasEntity rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/resource/Q38112"/>
        <ontology:hasEntity rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/resource/Q576355"/>
        <ontology:hasEntity rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/resource/Q646107"/>
        <ontology:is_identified_by rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/appellation/Innovation"/>
        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N32_VC_02_IT"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/44.012692123134684_10.29986561750469"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Endogenous. The production of chestnut flour is done in a traditional way but in the last ten years some innovation have interessed the roasted and peeled process, the marketing strategies( new packaging, use of social network) and the organization system. The innovation is related to New processes and New marketing strategies. The land use systems involved are Forestry. The local assets include Cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


