        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 28400. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 9919.9. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 1.16%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 29.68%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 69.17%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 31400. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 105293.3. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 2.39%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 25.06%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 72.55%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


